rows.label: qev087003_MSG0001
rows.name: This should be the fortress mainframe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087003_MSG0003
rows.name: I can try, but I wouldn't bother holding your breath.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087003_MSG0004
rows.name:
Even if I can, it'll take time.
Better to pull the drive and analyze it later.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087003_MSG0005
rows.name:
All right. Let's run with that.
...Just as soon as we're done with them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087003_MSG0006
rows.name:
Let's take care of these goons first,
then we can retrieve the data.[ST:wait ]
